Dear Bitcoinwell Community,

We=E2=80=99re pleased to introduce an important step forward=E2=80=94driven=
 directly by your feedback and ongoing engagement.

In recent months, many of you have asked for a more secure, reliable, and d=
edicated way to interact with your Bitcoinwell wallets beyond the browser. =
We=E2=80=99ve taken that input seriously. Today, we=E2=80=99re introducing =
the first version of the Bitcoinwell Wallet Desktop App, built to provide a=
 more controlled and dependable experience.

  What This Means for You

The Bitcoinwell Wallet Desktop App is designed to enhance both security and=
 usability, giving you greater confidence and efficiency when managing your=
 digital assets.

Key improvements include:

 Crossplatform availability: Compatible with Windows, macOS, and Linux envi=
ronments
 Secure interaction layer: A dedicated desktop environment that reduces rel=
iance on browserbased risks
 Chromium compatibility: Seamless support for all Chromiumbased integration=
s
 Improved performance: Faster load times and more stable operations
 Wallet compatibility: Supports BTC and participating crypto wallets connec=
ted to the ongoing Midnight Token initiative

  A Stronger Focus on Security

Security continues to be a central priority. Moving to a desktopbased exper=
ience allows for a more controlled environment, helping reduce exposure to =
browser vulnerabilities while offering a more consistent interaction layer =
for your wallet activities.

This direction also aligns with our recent updates and communications, wher=
e we=E2=80=99ve emphasized strengthening infrastructure and improving user =
confidence across all touchpoints.

  Midnight Token Participation

The app is fully aligned with the current Midnight Token activity, which re=
mains active for the next two weeks. Using the desktop app ensures a smooth=
er and more reliable way to participate without unnecessary interruptions.

  Getting Started

To begin:

1. Download the desktop app: https://www.bitcoinwell.io/
2. Install it on your device
3. Open the application and connect your wallet
4. Begin using a more secure and streamlined experience

  Ongoing Feedback

This is an early release, and your feedback remains essential. If you encou=
nter limitations or have suggestions for improvement, we encourage you to s=
hare them. Your input plays a direct role in shaping future updates and enh=
ancements.



We remain committed to building tools that reflect the needs of our communi=
ty=E2=80=94balancing usability, security, and longterm reliability. Thank y=
ou for your continued support and for being an active part of Bitcoinwell=
=E2=80=99s progress.

Warm regards,
The Bitcoinwell Team
